-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">얼마나 심각하고 마음이 아픈 일이냐?</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">너희가 이것을 깨닫고&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">진정 네 주관을 버리고 네 생각과 뜻을 버리고&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">나의 뜻을 따라오너라!</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">무엇을 행해야 할지 모르겠으면&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-fami